org.cpsolver.studentsct.model

Class Config

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment.context.AbstractClassWithContext<Request,Enrollment,Config.ConfigContext>
      • org.cpsolver.studentsct.model.Config
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CanHoldContext, CanInheritContext<Request,Enrollment,Config.ConfigContext>, HasAssignmentContext<Request,Enrollment,Config.ConfigContext>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OnlineConfig

    public class Config
extends AbstractClassWithContext<Request,Enrollment,Config.ConfigContext>
implements CanInheritContext<Request,Enrollment,Config.ConfigContext>
    Representation of a configuration of an offering. A configuration contains id, name, an offering and a list of subparts.

    Each instructional offering (see Offering) contains one or more configurations. Each configuration contain one or more subparts. Each student has to take a class of each subpart of one of the possible configurations.

    Version:
